{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"efd1b7ffcd","title":"关于经学问题给范文澜的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"80516f0e44","index":0,"year":1940,"month":9,"day":5,"articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"范文澜","id":"c772040b7d","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji2","name":"毛泽东文集第二卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji2.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji2":{"comments":[{"id":"5809c26028","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据手稿刊印。"},{"id":"2b5129e9ec","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":10,"text":"范文澜（一八九三——一九六九），浙江绍兴人。当时任延安马列学院历史研究室主任。"},{"id":"feb8d8d25c","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":2,"text":"指范文澜一九四○年在延安新哲学会年会上关于中国经学简史的讲演提纲。这个提纲后经整理于同年连续发表在延安《中国文化》第二卷第二、第三期上，题为《中国经学史的演变》。"},{"id":"fbb8b98896","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","publication":{},"article":{},"index":3,"part_index":2,"offset":127,"text":"康、梁、章、胡，指康有为（一八五八——一九二七，广东南海人）、梁启超、章炳麟、胡适。他们都是在近代中国经学史和思想史上有重大影响的学者。"},{"id":"1e26adaac1","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","publication":{},"article":{},"index":4,"part_index":2,"offset":151,"text":"廖平（一八五二——一九三二），四川井研人，中国近代经学家。吴虞（一八七一——一九四九），四川新繁（今属新都）人，五四运动前后曾写文章批判旧礼教，后来很少发表新见。叶德辉（一八六四——一九二七），湖南湘潭人，是维护封建统治的古文学者。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d16e8bcb76","type":"title","text":"关于经学问题给范文澜的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2b5129e9ec","type":"appellation","text":"文澜同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"feb8d8d25c","type":"paragraph","text":"提纲读了，十分高兴，倘能写出来，必有大益，因为用马克思主义清算经学这是头一次，因为目前大地主大资产阶级的复古反动十分猖獗，目前思想斗争的第一任务就是反对这种反动。你的历史学工作继续下去，对这一斗争必有大的影响。第三次讲演因病没有听到，不知对康、梁、章、胡的错误一面有所批判否？不知涉及廖平、吴虞、叶德辉等人否？越对这些近人有所批判，越能在学术界发生影响。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fbb8b98896","type":"paragraph","text":"我对历史完全无研究，倘能因你的研究学得一点，深为幸事。致以敬礼！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1e26adaac1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c4ff441b6","type":"paragraph","text":"九月五日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"efd1b7ffcd","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":309,"end":309}}}},"__N_SSG":true}